pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Brain Mushroom 75g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

An organic 5 mushroom health blend with zinc derived from Guava to support healthy cognitive function.

Wanderlust Brain Mushroom is a consciously created,
organic 5 mushroom wholefood health blend. With zinc derived
from Guava to support brain health by maintaining healthy
cognitive function.

Size: 75 g NET

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Wanderlust Organic Mushroom Blend* (83.8%) [Shiitake mushroom powder*, Enokitake mushroom powder*, Oyster mushroom powder*, Trumpet mushroom powder*, Brown rice powder*, Maitake mushroom powder*], Organic Guava fruit powder* (16.2%).

*Organic ingredients

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, soy, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

SERVING SUGGESTION: Mix 1.84 g (½ a teaspoon) in 200 mL of water, hot beverage or juice. Alternatively, add to a smoothie or sprinkle onto salad, soups or meals.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry
place away from direct heat
and sunlight. Do not use if
inner seal is missing or broken.
